  "body": "https://discord.com/channels/694822223575384095/782670046736285697/1030814583771889724\n\nTo be able to plan times to restart, it might be useful to have a metric that displays a countdown in seconds to the next duty ... or something similar...\n\nThe idea is that you'd then be able to potentially restart teku while you have a gap, but we also had a discussion about how timings may be fairly tight on a VC...\n\nCreated this ticket as a placeholder for discussion of this option.",
