    "body": "just a gauge? If we have duties in slot 3,4,5, then its just the slot time of slot 3 that would be the metric....\r\n\r\nAlso, if one duty is due at the end of the epoch (only scheduled duty), and we're in slot 1 of the epoch, then you'll be setting the next duty time as that slot 31 time...\r\n\r\nI'm pretty sure we won't have periods with no duties, maybe at startup... Maybe just letting it be set once a duty comes in would be fine in that scenario...\r\n\r\nWhat i don't want is a bunch of numbers, that would defeat the purpose... i think just 1 value, and if we can somehow have it be able to be on a dashboard as a time? that might inform the direction of if this would even work...",
